{
  "stem": "12810.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was worried always.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time he-- he give us food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He give us some food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that-- I-- I go to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But even where I go to him daytime-- if I go to him, I can wear the star.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But after 6 o'clock or something-- I don't remember-- 5 or 6 o'clock-- I had to take off the star, or I can't go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because he was not a Jew anymore, and his wife was a-- a born Catholic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he was a mixed marriage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He don't need to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's why he was thinking if nothing will happen to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But unfortunately, it is happen to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when that Hungarian [NON-ENGLISH] come to--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--power, yes, they take Miklos Horthy off, and that-- then they take him away and kill him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- [LAUGHS] the Hungarian films there, because no American film coming anymore, not overseas films; and, of course, the all operettes, and things, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we loved to see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went with my girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, because my mother cousins had three movie theater in Ujpest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a wealthy family, and I don't need to pay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So we go-- I take my girlfriends, and we go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And where a new film come, we was there-- the first to see it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the Al Jolson, the and Sonja Henie with the--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--ice skating.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I love it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We love it; and that was big things; and Spencer Tracy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And oh, my sweetheart was Nelson Eddy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We even put our pocket money together and send him a letter to send us a photo.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we 10 girls, we get one photo from Eddy Nelson.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
